troubleshouting build itself:
-----------------------------
perfect-scrollbar:
  Fix the version (package.json) to 0.8.1, because 1.x (without jQuery) need different usage (and different .css path in gulpfile.js).
select2 reports "No.../some special feattures/":
  Need full select2 version:
  "main": "dist/js/select2.js" -> "main": "dist/js/select2.full.js"
select2.i18n fails in e.define:
  https://stackoverflow.com/questions/39649078/select2-requirejs-cannot-bundle-i18n-files/57526305#57526305
  I have patched en.js, cs.js,.. in node_modules/select2/dist/js/i18n/ based on the comment from Tschallacka:
  .amd) -> .amd){
  }(); -> }else{window.setTimeout(arguments.callee,10);}})();


